nodes.text: Attack of the Clones Read-Along Storybook and CD

Attack of the Clones Read-Along Storybook and CD is a young readers' story from Disney–Lucasfilm Press, released on February 7, 2017. It presents an illustrated version of the story of Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones with an accompanying CD with narration of the story and character voices.
Relive all of the excitement of Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones in this illustrated storybook-and-CD set.
